  <h1>MindM8 – Account Deletion Policy</h1>

  <p>This page explains how users of <strong>MindM8</strong> can permanently delete their account and all associated data.</p>

  <h2>👤 App & Developer Info</h2>
  <p><strong>App:</strong> MindM8 – AI Journaling Bestie<br>
     <strong>Developer:</strong> Oryvo AI</p>

  <h2>🗑️ How to Delete Your Account</h2>
  <p>You can delete your account at any time by requesting thorugh email:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Users just need to send an email with acount deletion request to oryvoai@gmail.conm</li>
    <li>A Delete acount button will be introduced soon within the app</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>💥 What Happens When You Delete Your Account</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Your account is permanently deleted from our Firebase Authentication system</li>
    <liAll chat entries, GPT conversations, and personal data are deleted from Firestore</li>
    <li>You will lose all progress and saved content</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>⏳ Processing Time</h2>
  <p>Account deletion requests are typically processed within <strong>24-72 hours</strong> of submission.</p>

  <h2>📬 Need Help?</h2>
  <p>If you’re unable to access the app or facing issues, email us at: <strong>oryvoai@gmail.com</strong></p>
